column1: OMAP-36: Organ Mapping Antibody Panel (OMAP) for Multiplexed Antibody-Based Imaging of Human Heart with MICS
Author Name(s): Christoph Herbel; Salpy Baghdo; Julia Femel

column24: rationale
CD45 broadly labels all hematopoietic cells and can be used to assess immune infiltration.
NPPA (Natriuretic peptide A) is a cardiac hormone secreted by atrial cardiomyocytes, but is not expressed by ventricular cardiomyocytes.
CD14 is expressed by macrophages and to a much lesser extent by neutrophils and dendritic cells.
In cardiac tissue, CD34 is expressed on a subsets of endothelial cells and stromal cells, such as telocytes.
VE-cadherin is expressed by endothelial cells and used as a marker for blood vessels.
Myosin regulatory light chain 2, atrial isoform, is highly expressed by cardiomyocytes of the cardiac muscle atrium.
CD68 is a lysosomal glycoprotein and used to identify myeloid cells including macrophages.
Vimentin is expressed in mesenchymal cells, such as fibroblasts.
PLP1 (Myelin proteolipid protein) is expressed by cells of the nervous system, such as oligodendrocytes.
Calponin-1 is expressed in smooth muscle cells and has several actin binding sites.
Sialoadhesin (CD169) is expressed by macrophages, including resident cardiac macrophages.
Troponin T is expressed by cardiomyocytes, both atrial and ventricular.
S100A8 is expressed in myeloid cells, such as monocytes, dendritic cells and neutrophils. It forms a heterocomplex with S100A9.
S100A9 is expressed in myeloid cells, such as monocytes, dendritic cells and neutrophils. It is the binding partner of S100A8.
Alpha smooth muscle actin is expressed by smooth muscle cells of coronary arteries and veins.
CD31 is expressed by endothelial cells and used as a marker for blood and, to a lesser degree, lymphatic vessels.
The human leukocyte antigens of the major histocompatibility complex (MHC) class I are expressed by all human nucleated cells.
Collagen type III is a protein of the extracellular matrix and expressed by endothelial cells of the blood vessels, smooth muscle cells and fibroblasts.
